      <title>真主党首领称对以战斗进入“新阶段”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/hezbollah-chief-says-battle-against-israel-enters-new-phase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的真主党领导人表示，该组织与以色列的战斗已进入新阶段，并誓言在该激进组织高级指挥官在贝鲁特被杀后作出回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/hezbollah-chief-says-battle-against-israel-enters-new-phase</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
