    <item>
      <title>伊朗埋葬哈马斯高级官员，以色列准备报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领袖带领人们在本周于德黑兰被暗杀的哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的灵柩前进行祈祷，与此同时，以色列军方提高了对潜在报复性袭击的警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普未能解除禁言令，称此举将给哈里斯带来助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-says-gag-order-gives-harris-unfair-felon-attack-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约上诉法院驳回了唐纳德·特朗普提出的解除封口费刑事案件中针对他的禁言令的请求，特朗普表示，该禁言令阻止他全面回应卡马拉·哈里斯的说法，即 11 月 5 日的选举是在检察官和“被定罪的重罪犯”之间的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-says-gag-order-gives-harris-unfair-felon-attack-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两名摩尔多瓦公务员因从事俄罗斯间谍活动被拘留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/two-moldovan-civil-servants-detained-for-spying-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地检察官在一份声明中表示，在议会遭到突袭后，两名摩尔多瓦公务员在该国首都基希讷乌被拘留，罪名是叛国罪和为外国密谋罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/two-moldovan-civil-servants-detained-for-spying-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
